<h3>Job Openings:</h3>
<hr />
<h4>Childcare Position: Nursery (Birth&ndash;Age 2)</h4>
<p>Do you love working with young children? The early childhood department at Portland Christian Center is looking for a few part-time paid nursery workers. PCC is a dynamic mid-sized church with activities and programs throughout the week that require qualified care takers.</p>
<p>The positions are for 5-10 hours per week; flexible schedule required.</p>
